I'm gonna make a statement from the dock.
我打算在被告席上发表申明。

452
00:49:48,510 --> 00:49:52,380
For God's sake, Nelson! If you make a statement from the dock, 
看在上帝的份上，纳尔逊！如果您在被告席上发表申明，

453
00:49:52,450 --> 00:49:54,220
you'll lose your right to be cross-examined.
这样你就丧失了向对方证人反讯问的权利。

454
00:49:54,285 --> 00:49:57,855
You might as well admit the charges. I am admitting the charges.
你倒不如承认所有控罪。我都会认罪。

455
00:50:00,290 --> 00:50:08,230
Show me this statement.
给我看看你的申明。

456
00:50:16,508 --> 00:50:17,888
You damn fool!
你这该死的傻瓜！

457
00:50:18,280 --> 00:50:19,888
Cut the last sentence at least.
删除最后一句话，至少。

458
00:50:20,310 --> 00:50:22,300
Don't give it to them on a plate.
不要轻易地交给他们。

459
00:50:22,450 --> 00:50:24,350
This is not for them.
这不是为了他们。

460
00:50:25,480 --> 00:50:27,350
It's for our people.
这是为我们人民。

461
00:50:28,008 --> 00:50:48,999
If I'm going to die, I want them to know why.
如果我就要死了，我也希望他们知道为什么。【著名的法庭申明开始！】

462
00:50:49,510 --> 00:50:51,410
My name is Nelson Mandela.
我的名字是纳尔逊・曼德拉。

463
00:50:52,380 --> 00:50:54,310
I'm the first accused.
我是第一被告。

464
00:50:56,280 --> 00:51:00,240
I do not deny that I had planned sabotage.
我不否认我策划过破坏活动。

465
00:51:00,350 --> 00:51:09,420
I did not planned it in the spirit of recklessness,nor because I have any love for violence.
但我不是在鲁莽中策划的，也不是因为我爱好暴力。

466
00:51:09,530 --> 00:51:17,330
The hard facts of that 50 years of non-violence have brought the African people
残酷的事实是50年非暴力带给非洲人民的

467
00:51:17,400 --> 00:51:21,460
nothing but more and more repressive legislations
只是越来越多的压制性法律

468
00:51:21,510 --> 00:51:24,300
and fewer and fewer rights.
和越来越少的权利。

469
00:51:24,410 --> 00:51:31,320
Africans want a just share in the whole of South Africa.
非洲人想要公平地分享整个南非。

470
00:51:31,420 --> 00:51:37,250
We want equal political rights: One man, one vote.
我们想要平等的政治权利:一人一票。【全民普选】

471
00:51:37,420 --> 00:51:41,320
I've dedicated myself to this struggle of the African people.
我一直全身心地投入非洲人的这一项斗争。

472
00:51:41,390 --> 00:51:45,330
I have fought against white domination.
我反对白人霸权。

473
00:51:45,460 --> 00:51:49,260
I have fought against black domination.
我反对黑人霸权。【超越种族，超越仇恨，超越血仇】

474
00:51:49,470 --> 00:51:54,410
I have cherished the ideal of a free democratic society,
我一直抱有一个自由、民主社会的理想，【南非梦】


475
00:51:54,440 --> 00:51:59,340
where all persons live together in harmony with equal opportunities，
在那个社会里: 各种族和谐生活，拥有平等的机会，

476
00:52:00,450 --> 00:52:06,280
it is an ideal which I hope to live for and achieve,
这就是我希望为之而生存并要实现的理想

477
00:52:06,420 --> 00:52:09,440
but if needs be,
但如果需要的话，

478
00:52:10,260 --> 00:52:27,009
it is an ideal for which I am prepared to die.
这也是一个我准备为之献身的理想。【为民主自由献身】

479
00:52:22,310 --> 00:52:30,470
Amandla!-Ngawethu           
Power政权!-To the people归民!

480
00:52:31,480 --> 00:52:53,888
Mayibuye!--Africa!
Return!归还!--非洲!

481
00:52:57,270 --> 00:53:02,260
Before the judge imposes the supreme penalty, there is one more step.
在法官宣判极刑之前，还有一个程序。

482
00:53:02,340 --> 00:53:07,330
He will ask the first accused Nelson, "have you any reason to advance
他会问第一被告纳尔逊，“你还能提出什么原因

483
00:53:07,410 --> 00:53:09,440
where the death sentence should not be passed?"
