490
00:53:41,350 --> 00:53:45,340
I've reached my verdict. The defendants will rise.
我已经做出判决。全体８名被告请起立。

491
00:53:49,390 --> 00:53:52,450
The accused are all found guilty as charged.
被告全都如原控，被判有罪。

492
00:53:56,330 --> 00:54:00,260
