493
00:54:00,330 --> 00:54:03,500
In essence... they have entered martyrdom
实质上，他们已经为其信念殉道

494
00:54:04,270 --> 00:54:07,360
at the hands of what they call their oppressors.
在他们称之为压迫者的手中成为烈士。

495
00:54:07,470 --> 00:54:11,500
But I would not give them that satisfaction.
但我不会让他们就此圆满。

496
00:54:12,310 --> 00:54:17,008
Let us show the world that we are a nation of laws
让我们向世界展示：我们是法制国家

497
00:54:17,088 --> 00:54:22,350
and when possible we can pair justice with mercy.
并且我们尽可能让公正与仁慈同在。

498
00:54:22,490 --> 00:54:27,480
I therefore decided not to impose the supreme penalty.
我因此决定：不判处最高处罚【极刑】

499
00:54:31,400 --> 00:54:41,330
The sentence in the case of all their dues will be life imprisonment.
根据本案，数罪并罚，判他们的：终身监禁。

